<p>This is a great start! Broadly this palette contains a variety of colors that are quite different. However Charity Pink and Berry are a bit close, so are Maroon and Heather Cardinal as well as Gold and Maize Yellow.</p>
<p>Lets make a heatmap showing how similar/different the colors are and take a closer look:</p>
<div class="quarto-figure quarto-figure-center">
